  • public class watchDog
extends Hero
    Date: May 12th 2018 watchDog describes and creates a type of hero, Watch Dog. Watch Dog's parent class is Hero. This Hero Type has the ability to prevent undesirable Random Events Occurring when the Team travels.
    Author:
    Sachin Sakthivel and Sasiru Goonatillake
